FBIS3-49639 "dreeu009_a_94002" FBIS-EEU-94-009 Document Type:Daily Report 13 Jan 1994 ALBANIA Kosovar Association Assists Satellite Program AU1201191594 Tirana TVSH Television Network in Albanian 1900 GMT 11 Jan 94 AU1201191594 Tirana TVSH Television Network Language: Albanian Article Type:BFN [Text] Financial aid for the satellite program of the Albanian Radio-Television. The Albanian Cultural Association Dardania, based in Mannheim in Germany, which is made up of Kosovar emigrants and acts as an independent association, as an Albanian chamber, is active in its solidarity with the aim of preserving our language, culture, and traditions. This Association has recently assisted the Albanian Radio-Television Satellite program with 3,505 German marks. The money was gathered by the Association led by its chairman, Mr. Idriz Hoti, and our compatriots. We thank them for this assistance.
